# ---- Build output ----
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# ---- NuGet packages (restore on build) ----
[Pp]ackages/
!packages/repositories.config
*.nupkg
**/packages/*

# ---- Visual Studio user-specific files ----
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs

# ---- Build results / temp ----
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
*.log
TestResults/

# ---- Secrets — DO NOT commit these ----
# Keep your real Web.config local; commit a template instead
Web.config
Web.*.config
# But allow the template:
!Web.config.template

# ---- ReSharper / other ----
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user